# Vue Data-Fetching Convention

Every list endpoint has a matching composable in `src/composables/`:
```
export function useArticles() {
  const data = ref([]); const error = ref(null); const loading = ref(false);
  const refresh = async (cursor) => { /* ... */ };
  return { data, error, loading, refresh };
}
```
- File name: `use<Resource>.ts`, kebab-case folder, camelCase file
- No direct fetch() in .vue files
- Composable handles cursor pagination internally
